\ip On papiakon paŇčdet kab…® da m…®Ňčat am…®nyokon Yesu dakon Gen Bin Tag…®si yawit b…®sapmon gen dubag…®si yawit. AŇčakwa m…®Ňčat am…®nyo morapm…® da Gen Bin Tag…®si uŇčun yolakwa paŇčmuwukbi si teban tag…®t.
\ip Papia on da yabekbi morapm…® da pi awit uŇčun do yosok. Mani Pita gat Pol gat da pi ag…®mal uŇčun do morapm…® yosok. Pita uŇčun Yesu dakon paŇčdetni k…®nda. Mani Pol kal…®p Yesu d…®ma yolg…®t. Pol mib…®ltok Kristo dakon paŇčmuwukbi pab…®Ňč yop do pi tebaisi ag…®t. Mani don Yesu da Pol yaŇč …®ban but tob…®l aŇček pi am…®ni bam…®si k…®nda dagag…®t. AŇček Am…®n ŇäwakŇčwar…® Kab…®kon PiŇčkop gen yoy…®g…®t.
\ip On papiagwan Luk da Pol da yo morap ag…®t do yaŇček ‚Äúnin da ag…®maŇč‚ÄĚ yaŇč yosok. Nandak nandak am…®n morapm…® da yaŇč nandaŇč: Luk iy…® Pol gat b…®sap d…® ag…®pgumal do ‚Äúnin da ag…®maŇč‚ÄĚ yaŇč uŇčun do yosok.
