\v 26 \x - \xo 28:26 \xt Ais 6.9-10\x* ‚ÄėGak k…®Ňč on am…®n kab…® yaŇč yoy…®ki: Ji b…®sap morapm…®si gen nandakdaŇč, mani mib…®l…® d…®ma nandaba p…®sokd…®sak.
